	<td width="98%">
  
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
		<tr>
		    <td valign="top">
		     <p><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Article Title:</b>&nbsp;</font>
		     <font face="Verdana" size="2">Sword of the Gathering</font><br>
		     <a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=357448" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
		
		<tr><td>&nbsp;</tr><tr>
		
		    <td valign="top">
		    <p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    <blockquote>Here's some screenshots of the <b>Sword of the Gathering</b> that some people won at the Fan Faire.</p>

<p>Thanks to all the Rangers in my group who all got grade 1 migraines trying to remember all the 2hs weapons, zones, quests, spells for the trivia contest.</p>
<p><a href=http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?ID=357451 target=_blank>Full View</a><br><a href=http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?ID=357453 target=_blank>Hilt Close-Up<br><a href=http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?ID=357454 target=_blank>Stat's</a></p>
<p><b><i>Aethdor Stoutheart</b></i><br>
40th Season Ranger<br>
Officer United Powers of Norrath<br>
Lanys T'Vyl</p></blockquote>
Congratulations to all of the quest winners of this sick weapon at the Fan Faire!
		    </font></p>
			 </td>
